com.jess.arms.widget.photoview

类 PhotoViewAttacher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jess.arms.widget.photoview.PhotoViewAttacher
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    android.view.View.OnLayoutChangeListener, android.view.View.OnTouchListener

    public class PhotoViewAttacher
extends Object
implements android.view.View.OnTouchListener, android.view.View.OnLayoutChangeListener
    The component of PhotoView which does the work allowing for zooming, scaling, panning, etc. It is made public in case you need to subclass something other than ImageView and still gain the functionality that PhotoView offers
